{"word":"ἄμπελος","slug":"ἄμπελος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄμπελος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:perhaps'>Perh.</a>from <el>ἀμπί</el> (aeolic for <a href='S:ἀμφί'><el>ἀμφί</el></a>), <el>ἕλιξ</el>, from its <i>clasping tendrils</i>.\n<p/><i>a vine</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>vitis</el>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/>"}]}